# Groq API key for the website AI assistant — get one at https://console.groq.com/keys
#
# This key is used ONLY on the server (the /api/chat serverless function and the Vite
# dev middleware). It is intentionally NOT prefixed with VITE_, so Vite never inlines it
# into the public client bundle. Keep it secret.
#
# Local dev:    put it in a local .env file (this folder) — already gitignored.
# Production:   add it in your host's dashboard as an Environment Variable named
#               GROQ_API_KEY (Vercel: Project → Settings → Environment Variables).
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
